怕”，当妈的还一直托举并“加油”，直到孩子双手滑脱“蹭”了下来喊“疼”，您的心也真大!还有这位老人家，虽说今年是猴年，也不能逮树就上啊，那树都快折了，旁边的孩子也都看着您呢。</p></div>  <footer>  <p class=tip_quick>文章内容由搜索引擎自动发现并显示为快照，不代表360新闻的立场和观点，<a target=_blank class=viewsource href="http://news.cnr.cn/tj/20160321/t20160321_521668495.shtml">查看原文</a></p>      </footer> </article> <section class=sohu_cy> <div id=SOHUCS sid='3c95f4b2a1852fcc552b549868a01296'></div><script id=changyan_mobile_js charset="utf-8" src="http://changyan.sohu.com/upload/mobile/wap-js/changyan_mobile.js?client_id=cyrTywwWs&conf=prod_c56aa5a54e89138d855c5ca9b31470a0" ></script> </section>  <aside id="next-news"> <h3><em>踹树制造樱花雨</em>的其它新闻:</h3> <ul>    <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E8%B8%B9%E6%A0%91%E5%88%B6%E9%80%A0%E6%A8%B1%E8%8A%B1%E9%9B%A8&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=6&amp;m=87a6d986a0c30349d7615e08086d42b55b7d461f&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnr.cn%2Fnative%2Fgd%2F20160321%2Ft20160321_521665865.shtml" data-pos="1"> 曝南京游人为制"<b>樱花雨</b>"爬树或用脚<b>踹树</b>(图) </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E8%B8%B9%E6%A0%91%E5%88%B6%E9%80%A0%E6%A8%B1%E8%8A%B1%E9%9B%A8&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=7&amp;m=d54d0651e7642c1a4468f146d421301e5b0b2109&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fjiangsu.china.com.cn%2Fhtml%2Fjsnews%2Faround%2F4903727_1.html" data-pos="2"> 南京游人被曝制"<b>樱花雨</b>":爬树或用脚<b>踹树</b> </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E8%B8%B9%E6%A0%91%E5%88%B6%E9%80%A0%E6%A8%B1%E8%8A%B1%E9%9B%A8&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=8&amp;m=2596a6e356ba920fbd9ea918c0c32acbe2bdffe6&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fjiangsu.china.com.cn%2Fhtml%2F2016%2Fkuaixun_0321%2F4888427.html" data-pos="3"> 南京:游客被曝为制"<b>樱花雨</b>"攀爬或用脚<b>踹树</b> </a>  </ul> </aside>  <div class=mask style="display:none"></div> <div class="open-in-browser-tip" style="display:none"> <p>好无奈，微信君不让直接下载，别担心，点击<b>右上角</b>，选择“<b>在浏览器中打开</b>”就能下载啦~</p> <a class=close href="javascript:;"><img src="http://p3.qhimg.com/d/inn/a8960a66/close.png"></a> </div><script>(function(){var e=document.getElementById("news-body"),t=e.getElementsByTagName("img");for(var n=0;n<t.length;n++)t[n].parentNode.tagName.toUpperCase()==="P"&&(t[n].par